[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] your teeth-gritting time.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]But obviously
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] it makes work for the NHS senior officers, who have completed the Adva
[normal]nced Gobbledegook course and are advised by private contractors,
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] You may not understand the result of your Missing Information Review.... But,
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] then again, you are not supposed to. So don't feel a failure if the reply is totally 
[normal]i
[normal]ncomprehensible.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]You
[normal]’
[normal]r
[normal]e
[normal] supposed to give up, as you are a defeated bereaved person who cannot cope with your grief and constantly being played by the Health Board at the same time.
